-- Global outlook "not so bad": IMF chief
-- 
-- Sat Dec 4, 2010 6:50am EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2010/12/04/us-imf-strausskahn-idUSTRE6B310Q20101204

 

 BRUSSELS  (Reuters) - The global economic outlook is "not so bad," the International Monetary Fund's managing director Dominique Strauss-Kahn said on Saturday. 

 Speaking to the Belgian parliament, he also said that Europe's recovery was still "sluggish."